description:
What’s up gurls!

Long time no see!! I’ve been preparing this mashup since “Kill This Love” was released, but I got a job and I got no time at all for doing it before… So I’m sorry, I’m afraid it will be like this for a long time, excepting holidays, although I don’t know what I’ll do then…

Well, KTL has a 1/3 beat (rhythm), and the only EDM song I know and it’s so famous btw is “I’m An Albatraoz”, which I LOVE so much.

Albatraoz hasn’t a dynamic melody, so it sounds a little monotone for this mix, so I made my own melody on Rosé/Jisoo parts. I hope you like it, that’s how would sound a real original remix 100% by me.

On the Jennie-Lisa part, I used “Non Non Non (Rob & Chris Remix)” by Lolita Jolie, because I love that melody, and I think it fits well. I edited the rhythm from 1/4 beat to the 1/3 beat just cutting and moving sounds.

The final drop sounded so monotone if I had left like it was, so I preferred to use a trap remix of Albatraoz, and I think it fits perfectly, just leave me your opinion on the comment section bellow (if you’ve read ‘till here LOL).
I hope you like this unexpected surprise on the last drop x)

I hope you liked it! ♥

▶ Music Video: https://youtu.be/rFMBXas6i1Y
🎨 More details about the cover on DeviantArt: http://fav.me/dd7pa8e

description:
Hey people!

Long time no see!

Copyright has blocked me here for so much time, but now I think I can comeback here with some restrictions!

Here you have my new mashup between BLACKPINK and SaberZ!!

First of all, happy World Pride!! For all those LGBT+ people who follow my channel and the ones who not! Never stop fighting for our rights as human beings! Remember, LOVE WINS! 💪🏻🏳️🌈

Okay, now I bring you something special! It’s just an explosion of feelings in this Remix/Mashup, especially for all those EDM lovers like me! Even if you’re not EDM lover, you’ll remember the old style of BLACKPINK, ‘cause this track is under Big Room genre (the same genre as Boombayah), which I love and it’s my favorite genre, although it’s not as trendy as before… But you know, as Bassjakers and Hardwell said… #BigRoomNeverDies!!!

Alright, I was looking for some EDM tracks for give BLACKPINK the essence that I’ve always loved from them… We’ve been waiting for so much for their comeback, and they’ve promoted Ddu-Du Ddu-Du the most (with a MV for only that song), although I pretty love Forever Young in their new album Square Up… But anyways I still love them, they’re my favorite girl-band in Korea and in the world xD

I hope you liked it! ♥

🎥 Music Video: https://youtu.be/sDqTIsw_-Sk
🎨 More details about the cover on DeviantArt: http://fav.me/dcgspsp
